OL,3,CParamedic 'has flashbacks' to
OL,4,Cschoolboy drowning
OL,6,FA paramedic who was called out to a
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire reservoir when a 16-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy drowned three years ago
OL,9,Fsays he remembers the incident "as if
OL,10,Fit was yesterday".
OL,12,FDarren Thorpe, a member of the
OL,13,FHazardous Area Response Team, said he
OL,14,Fstill has flashbacks to the scene of
OL,15,Fthe tragedy at Ulley Reservoir in
OL,16,Fwhere Sam Haycock died.
OL,18,F"I can still remember seeing his
OL,19,Funiform folded up at the side of the
OL,20,Freservoir, it will never leave me," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
