OL,3,CParamedic 'has flashbacks' to
OL,4,Cschoolboy drowning
OL,6,FMr Thorpe joined a water safety event
OL,7,Fat Clifton Park in Rotherham organised
OL,8,Fby Sam's father Simon Haycock aimed at
OL,9,Fgetting the message across that cold
OL,10,Fwater kills.
OL,12,F"I'm giving up my time because of that
OL,13,Fday, because I want to help Sam's dad
OL,14,Fand I want to talk to people about not
OL,15,Fgetting into the water."
OL,17,F"Even though the water looks tempting
OL,18,Fwhen it's warm, the reservoir isn't,
OL,19,Fit's cold. It's not safe," he said.
