OL,3,CParamedic 'has flashbacks' to
OL,4,Cschoolboy drowning
OL,6,FFigures from the National Water Safety
OL,7,FForum show that since Sam Haycock died
OL,8,Fin 2021 the number of accidental
OL,9,Fdrownings has risen.
OL,11,FLast year in the UK there were 236
OL,12,Fdeaths, ten more than in 2022.
OL,14,FSam's father Simon said he wanted
OL,15,Fsomething positive to come from his
OL,16,Fson's death and has set up Sam's Army
OL,17,FMission to spread the message about
OL,18,Fthe dangers of open water.
