OL,6,F"Three years after Sam died it's
OL,7,Freally hard. But rather than dwell on
OL,8,Fthe sad story about losing somebody to
OL,9,Fdrowning, we put an event on to try to
OL,10,Fshow to people what we're trying to do
OL,11,Fabout it," he said.
